     <td class="lower"><span class="style4">In accordance with the updated IRS guidelines regarding e-signatures for the 4506-T/4506T-EZ Request for Transcript of Tax Return forms, LexisNexis&reg; IRS Verify can now process electronically-signed 4506-T/4506T-EZs for customers <strong>who have an existing relationship with an e-signature provider</strong>.   This feature will be available on August 23, 2013.   IRS Verify customers will still have the option to continue to submit ink-signatures on the 4506-T/4506T-EZs and can choose whichever method best fits their internal processes.</span></td>
    </tr>
